         <div type="translation">
            <ab n="036">i. The array <supplied reason="subaudible" cert="low">of the Carians</supplied> set up your statue, prefect, giving a small reward for your benefactions; for, Anthemios, saving peoples and cities, you also rescued the order of the Carians, which was being destroyed, to whom <supplied reason="subaudible">the Carians</supplied> Beronikianos, occupying the seat of governor, gave instructions to make a marble statue.</ab>
            <ab n="144">ii. Light! Life! <persName key="Mary" type="divine" full="yes">M<ex>ary</ex>
               </persName> b<ex>ore</ex>
               <persName key="Christ" type="divine" full="yes">Ch<ex>rist</ex>
               </persName>.</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <p n="036">i. l. 1,  Perhaps <foreign xml:lang="grc">
                  <unclear reason="damage">Κα</unclear>ρ<unclear reason="damage">ῶ</unclear>ν σε φάλαγξ</foreign>, although this seems clumsily repetitious.</p>
            <p n="144">ii. There are traces around the cross which might be decoration or a monogram.</p>
            <p>ii. l. 1, perhaps <foreign xml:lang="grc">
                  <persName key="Christ" type="divine" full="yes">
                     <expan>
                        <abbr>Χ</abbr>
                        <ex>ριστὸν</ex>
                     </expan>
                  </persName>
                  <persName key="Mary" type="divine" full="yes">
                     <expan>
                        <abbr>Μ</abbr>
                        <ex>αρία</ex>
                     </expan>
                  </persName>
                  <expan>
                     <abbr>Γ</abbr>
                     <ex>εννᾳ</ex>
                  </expan>
               </foreign>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>For i. see discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="IV.4" target=".xml"/>. The man honoured is the PPO Anthemios (405-414; PLRE II, Anthemius 1).</p>
            <p>For ii. see discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="VIII.16" target=".xml"/> and <ref type="eAla-text" n="VIII.20" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
